            <p id="mainimg"><img src="http://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20150412/K10010045751_1504121946_1504121949_01_03.jpg" alt="記事タイトル"/><a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="showVideo(this);" id="k10010045751_201504121946_201504121949.mp4" class="playBT"></a></p>
